[
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Yo Brian, you catch that new single-leg RDL variation Coach Trey programmed this morning? My hamstrings are already filing a complaint \ud83d\ude05",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-19",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:30+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Bro yes. That eccentric tempo was no joke. Ethan kept asking why I was walking funny at breakfast.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-24",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:31+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002TOM"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha! How's he doing? Still playing rec league ball?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-23",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:32+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Yeah, spring season just ended. Kid's knee tracking is actually solid \u2014 been coaching him on landing mechanics. Paying off.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-09",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:33+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002TOM"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "That's awesome man. You using any of that with your return-to-sport cases at the clinic?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-21",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:34+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "All the time. Same cues, different athlete. Atlanta heat is ramping up too so I'm keeping an eye on load management for outdoor guys.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-11-27",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:35+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002TOM"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Makes sense. Hey you going to the APTA sports section webinar Thursday or is clinic too slammed?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-06",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:36+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Penciled in. Slow afternoon. Karen's got a late shift anyway so I'll catch the full thing.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-11-03",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T14:29:37+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002TOM"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Bro did you finally PR that clean this morning? Heard Buckhead had some heavy lifting on the board today \ud83c\udfcb\ufe0f",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-02",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:06:56+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hit 225. Missed 230 by an inch. Bar got forward on me, classic. Coach flagged it too.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-24",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:06:57+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003MARCUS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Oof. Mobility or just a bad pull? You been managing that thoracic extension or letting clinic life win?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-16",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:06:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Clinic life winning honestly. Back-to-back patients til 6 yesterday. Karen had Ethan at soccer so I skipped mobility work entirely.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-12-02",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:06:59+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003MARCUS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "That's how it starts man. You're literally a PT. You know what happens next \ud83d\ude02",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-08",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:07:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I know, I know. Don't @ me. Programming recovery block starting Monday. No exceptions.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-25",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:07:01+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003MARCUS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Good. Tell Ethan I said go score some goals. How old is he now, 10?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-12-17",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:07:02+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Just turned 11. Kid's got a real left foot on him. Might be the athlete of the family, don't tell Lily I said that.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-04",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T02:07:03+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003MARCUS"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Pulled a 405 deadlift PR at the 5:15 class this morning. Buckhead crew went nuts. That creatine load is finally doing work \ud83d\udcaa",
    "thread_ts": "2026-11-07",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:28:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "405?? Brian you're 43 \ud83d\ude02 ok ok respect tho. How's the lower back feeling post-lift?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-17",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:28:56+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004TAMIKA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Back's solid. Spent the last training block fixing my hip hinge \u2014 PT perks, I finally diagnosed my own problem. Two years late but still.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-27",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:28:57+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Lol love that. Does Karen even flinch anymore when you walk in at 6:30am smelling like a CrossFit gym?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-11-01",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:28:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004TAMIKA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "She's fully immune. Ethan thought the PR was cool though. Now he's asking to try CrossFit. Kid is 11 Tamika \ud83e\udd26",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-06",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:28:59+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Honestly? Let him scale it. Foundation work at that age is huge. Hey \u2014 are you going to the APTA Sports conference in October?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-01",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:29:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004TAMIKA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Planning on it. Lily's fall soccer schedule might blow it up but I'll make it work. You presenting this year?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-24",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:29:01+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Submitting my ACL return-to-sport protocol paper next week. Fingers crossed they accept it \ud83e\udd1e you should submit something too",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-07",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T16:29:02+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004TAMIKA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Darren \u2014 you said crew's there by 7. I'm at CrossFit Buckhead til 6:30, won't make it to the clinic before 7:15. That gonna hold up the turf install?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-10",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T19:17:10+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Nah we just need door access. Can someone let us in or leave a code?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-12-12",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T19:17:11+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005DARREN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Karen's dropping Ethan at school and passes right by Peak Performance. She can leave a spare key under the mat by 6:55. I'll text her now.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-16",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T19:17:12+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Perfect. We're starting in the performance bay anyway, adhesive needs 2hrs to set before we roll out. Shouldn't be an issue.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-11-21",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T19:17:13+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005DARREN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Good. I've got patients stacked from 8\u201312, so keep demo noise in the back corridor until at least 10. Non-negotiable.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-12-01",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T19:17:14+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Already done with demo \u2014 yesterday was the loud part. Today's clean work, you won't even know we're there.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-05",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T19:17:15+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005DARREN"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "What about the wall padding? Still tracking for Friday or did that shipment get pushed again?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-10-11",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T19:17:16+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "standard",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ships Thursday out of Charlotte, we'll install Friday afternoon. Should be fully done before your Monday patients. Green week.",
